# Face recognition and greeting app on .NET Core 3.1 and raspberry pi 4
Face app uses azure congnitive services.

## Setup
For setup use setup.bat.

# Using the CLI

List all groups
```
cli list groups -e https://westeurope.api.cognitive.microsoft.com -k {KEY}
```

List all persons in a group
```
cli list persons -e https://westeurope.api.cognitive.microsoft.com -k {KEY} -g "{NAME}"
```

Create a new persons
```
cli create -e https://westeurope.api.cognitive.microsoft.com -k {KEY} -g "{NAME}" -n "Jhon Doe" -p "C:\Pictures\Jhon Doe"
```

Delete persons
```
cli delete -e https://westeurope.api.cognitive.microsoft.com -k {KEY} -g "{NAME}" -n "Jhon Doe"
```
